---
name: '{{skill.slug}}'
description: '{{skill.name}} — {{skill.description}}'
---

<skill-activation CRITICAL="TRUE">
{{#if (eq skill.phase "core")}}
1. LOAD the FULL skill file from .forge/core/{{skill.slug}}/SKILL.md
{{else}}
1. LOAD the FULL skill file from .forge/skills/{{skill.phase}}/{{skill.slug}}/SKILL.md
{{/if}}
2. READ its entire contents - this contains the complete workflow instructions
3. LOAD runtime config from .forge/config.yaml
4. If the skill says "Follow ./workflow.md", LOAD that workflow.md file from the same directory
5. Execute the workflow steps exactly as specified
</skill-activation>
